"Please note that most of these symbols (notable exceptions are the logic symbols) do not "
"have a special meaning in _Maxima_ and therefore will be interpreted as ordinary "
"characters. If _Maxima_ is compiled using a Lisp that doesn’t support dealing with "
"Unicode characters they might cause an error message instead."
